replies.body:
Nocturne is what riot would call a "healthy assassin", and by that they mean freaking OP. 

the only sentence that should have both "weak" and "Nocturne" in it is "Nocturne is there to slay the weak", because he sure as hell is not weak. Yeah his first jungle run is a bit of a close shave, and if invaded then he has a bit of trouble, but his ganks are supreme.

"Daaaaaarknesssssss" - {{champion:56}}
